{"tid":264304,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[日本中伏系列] 係日本食飯俾人斬到一頸血","createTime":"2017-05-30T16:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T12:49:18.000Z","uid":16376,"like":24,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a48d4d280b48ad0e423222f52c8984ffd6a41e0","tid":264304,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:42:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n岩岩同個fd係日本行街<br />\n佢係日本長住 咁個陣又唔知食咩<br />\n咁岩佢又話有餐廳推介<br />\n我見佢好識食咁 咪話好好好 跟佢搵食<br />\n入到間野其實都唔錯 好似好高級 D架妹好好Service<br />\n又有按摩椅 岩岩行到好攰 坐上去都幾爽<br />\n然後餓到Menu都無睇 就隨便叫 我諗都唔會中伏既 <br />\n因為間野實係好似好高級<br />\n叫左Sake 海鮮湯 牛 烏冬 雞個D大路野 <br />\n同埋間野又似食雞出名 所以叫左照燒雞<br />\n牛入口即融 好有牛味<br />\n最後叫左串燒<br />\n同個fd吹水 食下野 飲下野 幾舒服<br />\n跟著屌你老味 埋單就知中伏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一碟牛     8000YEn<br />\n照燒雞柳 14000YEN<br />\n醬茶小食 7000YEN　<br />\n燒茄子　9000YEN<br />\n海鮮又無寫價 問佢又up一堆日文<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　　　　<br />\n<br />\n　　　　　然後加一加　但這個發現<br />\n<br />\n　　　　　破賬目我心中驚怕"},{"pid":"6abaef5a0fb14eaa5140073ef6bda8d9a1830fa1","tid":264304,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:43:53.000Z","msg":"你自己唔menu話人斬你?"},{"pid":"15d6e18303f1957315359d0d80e018ab690433f5","tid":264304,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:44:18.000Z","msg":"入得呢啲地方預咗架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc2a5055d842e70e3406845c17cd3a2021db735","tid":264304,"uid":46950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"算唔算有新意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959b843e191d7a3970336fb835d15381dd6c95cd","tid":264304,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T16:47:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入得呢啲地方預咗架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwhy預左"},{"pid":"ae264249af71123e6e662523fc39229183c3fa